title: Beautiful Things (Full Song on Tape Cassette)
description:
Download the WAV file as a Patreon: https://patreon.com/yuriwong
Watch the remix process here: https://youtu.be/q1TCF2DaJTI
Tape master of Beautiful Things (Walter Mitty) remix, done on Type I cassette on my dad's old tape deck. I didn't use the deck's Dolby noise reduction; it attenuates the highs too much to be enjoyable. I kinda like the noise anyway
